span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- why does this bring out a Or result, why can't it see the hc prop</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The job of <code>field_simp</code> is to clear denominators, not to solve this goal. <code>field_simp at h</code> is the same as <code>simp at h</code> here.</p>",
